transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hi, thank you for calling Viagra. How can I assist you?

Speaker 2: Yes, I had ordered one prescription of the generic Viagra, and all of a sudden they started sending refills after refills, and I didn't want any refills.

Speaker 2: So I got a hold of K.T. Goodrich, and he said, send them back to us, and we'll get you a refund.

Speaker 1: Let me search for you.

segments.text: Hi, thank you for calling Viagra. How can I assist you?
Yes, I had ordered one prescription of the generic Viagra,
and all of a sudden they started sending refills after refills, and I didn't want any refills.
So I got a hold of K.T. Goodrich, and he said, send them back to us, and we'll get you a refund.
